{"lemma":"حُزْنُ","slug":"حُزْنُ","root":"ح.ز.ن","root_slug":"ح-ز-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ز-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حُزْن","root":"حزن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":7,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":13},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7893","n7896","n7897","n7898","n7899","n7900","n7901"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D8%B2%D9%92%D9%86%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make sad, to sadden"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause to mourn or lament"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grieve","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grieve, to mourn, to lament"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become sorrowful, sad, or unhappy","examples":[{"text":"لَا تَحْزَنْ إِنَّ اللهَ مَعَنَا","english":"Do not grieve; indeed God is with us."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become rough"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become rugged and hard"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَزَنَ (ḥazana) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sadness, grief, sorrow","examples":[{"text":"رَأَيْتُ الدَّهْرَ مُخْتَلِفًا يَدُورُ -- فَلَا حُزْنٌ يَدُومُ وَلَا سُرُورُ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rugged and hard ground","examples":[{"text":"Hadith\nاللَّهُمَّ لَا سَهْلَ إِلَّا مَا جَعَلْتَهُ سَهْلًا وَأَنْتَ تَجْعَلُ ٱلْحَزْنَ إِنْ شِئْتَ سَهْلًا\nal-lahumma lā sahla ʔillā mā jaʕaltahu sahlan waʔanta tajʕalu l-ḥazna ʔin šiʔta sahlan","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَزِنَ (ḥazina) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sadness, grief"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"sad, sorrowful, grieved"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7893","headword_ar":"حَزِنَ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazanN","text_ar":"حَزَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtzn","text_ar":"احتزن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHz~n","text_ar":"تحزّن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHAzn","text_ar":"تحازن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he grieved, mourned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lamented;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was sorrowful, sad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for him"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Msb, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taHozano","text_ar":"لَا تَحْزَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taHozanuwA","text_ar":"لَا تَحْزَنُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [ix. 40, &c., and iii. 133], do not denote a prohibition of getting"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"does not come by the will of man: the real meaning is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do not thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye, that which engenders"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"do not thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye, acquire"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Er-Rághib. [But this requires consideration; or, rather, is not in every case admissible.])       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazanahu","text_ar":"حَزَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzonN","text_ar":"حُزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHznhu","text_ar":"احزنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(another person, S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an affair, or an event, or a case, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused him to be affected with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which see below; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grieved him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused him to mourn"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lament,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be sorrowful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sad"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (S, Msb, K:) accord. to Yz, (S,) the former is of the dial. of Kureysh; and the latter, of the dial. of Temeem: (S, Msb:) and so say Th and Az: (Msb, TA:) but the former is said to be the more approved: (TA:) or, accord. to AZ, the aor. of the former is used, but not the pret.; (Msb, TA;) and when the act is ascribed to God, the latter verb is used: Z, also, says that what is well known in usage is the employing the pret. of the latter and the aor. of the former: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHznhu","text_ar":"احزنهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made him"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haziyn","text_ar":"حَزِين"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazanahu","text_ar":"حَزَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in some copies of the K ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hz~nhu","text_ar":"حزّنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be in him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazanahu","text_ar":"حَزَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it caused him to fall into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazunati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"حَزُنَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzuwnapN","text_ar":"حُزُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstHznt","text_ar":"استحزنت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ground was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, rough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged and hard."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  One says also of a beast that is not easy to ride upon,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHozunu Alma$oYa","text_ar":"يَحْزُنُ المَشْىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is rough in pace"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi HuzuwnapN","text_ar":"فِيهِ حُزُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In him is roughness"},{"kind":"text","text":"in pace]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","Sb"]},{"entry_id":"n7896","headword_ar":"حَزْنٌ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rugged"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and hard"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged high ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazomN","text_ar":"حَزْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) good land, though hard, is not thus termed: (ISh:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzuwnN","text_ar":"حُزُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazonapN","text_ar":"حَزْنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazonN","text_ar":"حَزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) so too, as some say, does ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzuwnN","text_ar":"حُزُونٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with two dammehs; or, as others say, this is a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazonN","text_ar":"حَزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and you say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN Hazoniy~apN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ حَزْنِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazonN","text_ar":"حَزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land of a rugged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged and hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged and high, kind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","ISh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n7897","headword_ar":"حُزْنٌ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazanN","text_ar":"حَزَنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, S, K,) the former said by AA to be used when the nom. or gen. case is employed, and the latter when the accus. is employed; (TA;) or the former is a simple subst., and the latter an inf. n.; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grief, mourning, lamentation, sorrow, sadness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappiness; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suruwrN","text_ar":"سُرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~N","text_ar":"هَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~N","text_ar":"هَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to common usage, is for some evil that is expected to happen; whereas]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzonN","text_ar":"حُزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grief arising on account of an unpleasant event that has happened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on account of an object of love that has passed away;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraHN","text_ar":"فَرَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (El-Munáwee, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a roughness in the spirit, occasioned by grief:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHozaAnN","text_ar":"اَحْزَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [properly a pl. of pauc.; but] it has no other pl. (TA.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmu AlHuzoni","text_ar":"عَامُ الحُزْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The year"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of mourning;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which died Khadeejeh and Aboo-Tálib:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, Th, K:) so called by Mohammad. (IAar, Th.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHamodu lil~hi A@l~a*iy A^a*ohaba","text_ar":"الحَمْدُ لِلّهِ ا@لَّذِي اَذْهَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ean~aA AlHazana","text_ar":"عَنَّا الحَزَنَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xxxv. 31], is said to mean ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Praise be to God, who hath dispelled from us"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the anxiety"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~","text_ar":"هَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the morning and evening meals:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"all grieving anxiety of the means of subsistence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the grief of punishment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","S","K","TA","IAar","Th"]},{"entry_id":"n7898","headword_ar":"حَزَنٌ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzonN","text_ar":"حُزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7899","headword_ar":"حَزُنٌ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaziynN","text_ar":"حَزِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7900","headword_ar":"حَزِنٌ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaziynN","text_ar":"حَزِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7901","headword_ar":"حُزُنٌ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazonN","text_ar":"حَزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}